Entries.default: "They took him. For what? Botaro's the second this month."
"And they say the pittings aren't increasing. Do they lie to themselves? Or just to us?"
"I say Biha did right, leaving the Gullet. She went and did what she needed."
"I don't disagree. But the little waifs, how're they to make on?"
"And may Amira bring fortune to the twins she left to rot."
"I'll miss Biha and her ilk. It's too quiet without them. May they go find fortune."
"At this rate, who'll be left to suffer the Mataru's ire?"
